<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3236061>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Archilestes chocoanus sp. n., male holotype: (a) head, dorsal view; − (b) pterothorax, dorsal view; − (c) same, ventral view; − (d) pterothorax and abdominal segments 1 and 2 showing color pattern, right lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3236061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3236063>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Archilestes chocoanus sp.n., male holotype:(a) pos- terior right leg; − (b) left wings, ventral view; − (c) left posterior hamule, right lateral view; − (d) genital ligula, right lateral view;− (e) same, distal portion, ventral view; − (f) same, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3236063/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3339507>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Fig. 3. Archilestes chocoanus sp. n. [Figs a-c: male holotype, Fig. d: female allotype]: (a) distal portion of abdomen, lateral view; − (b) right circus, dorsal view (right), ventral view (left); − (c) paraprocts and right circus, ventral view; − (d) distal portion of abdomen, left lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3339507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

